title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
OB: When accessing the Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the parameters are not displayed.
EB: When accessing the Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the parameters should be displayed.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the application and navigate to the report section.
2. Open any report that has parameters.
3. Click on the 'Show Report Parameters' button.
4. Check if the default values for each parameter are displayed in the dialog.
